headline: Bunge Global: Discounted Today, Agribusiness Powerhouse Tomorrow
summary: Bunge Global trades at a discount with 26.3% upside potential, supported by the Viterra merger, 42.9% revenue growth prospects, and a 3.5% dividend yield. Learn more on BG stock here.
